        <IRI>#TTP</IRI>
        <Literal>Tactics, Techniques and Procedures (TTP) are representations of the behavior or modus operandi of cyber adversaries.

Source: https://stix.mitre.org/about/documents/STIX_Whitepaper_v1.1.pdf</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
