        <IRI>#ThreatActor</IRI>
        <Literal>ThreatActors are characterizations of malicious actors (or adversaries) representing a cyber attack threat including presumed intent and historically observed behavior.

Source: https://stix.mitre.org/about/documents/STIX_Whitepaper_v1.1.pdf</Literal>
